data.description: Come explore the most sought after model in the Compass 19 Community!  The Admiral model features lots of upgrades and extras and is only 3 years old! First floor entry with entry stairs to 2nd floor living level. 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, living room, dining room, kitchen with upgraded higher-end appliances, built in pantry & laundry closet.  Soaring cathedral ceilings let in tons of natural light. Primary bedroom is super spacious with an attached ensuite and huge walk-in closet. Your own private 2nd level patio for is ready for relaxing or entertaining. This unit has its OWN ATTACHED GARAGE as well! The community features amenities including pool, kayak launch dock, clubhouse, dog park, and work out room.  Just minutes from Peninsula Town Center, this gem offers quick access to interstates 64, 264 and 664.  There are only a handful of these models in the community, and NOW is your time to make this one yours! Call your agent TODAY to schedule your private showing!
